        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar rr = parseFloat(rr)\nvar hr = parseFloat(hr)\nvar bp = parseFloat(bp)\nvar age = parseFloat(age)\n\nvar score = rr + hr + bp + age \n\nvar risk\n\nif (score <= 20) {\n\trisk = 'Low'\n}\nelse if (score > 20) { \n\trisk = 'High'\n}\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk + ' risk'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'CART Score'   \n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: risk, \n    value_text: 'risk',\n    message: 'Risk of cardiac arrest within 48 hours'\n});",
